{"tid":47192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"野豬闖停機坪 機場特警盾牌陣制服","createTime":"2016-12-20T07:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T07:47:04.000Z","uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8442af8800c2a23e14bd658bfa35a5f4997b1a06","tid":47192,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:40:00.000Z","msg":"機場有野豬出沒，遭特警暗角盾牌制服！下午2時18時，香港赤鱲角國際機場停機坪近70號閘口對開，一頭野豬被發現在路面上狂奔，由於擔心會影響航班升降，驚動多名機場特警手持盾牌到場，並將其逼入一角。由讀者拍得的相片可見，該隻野豬已被至少4名特警，以3個盾牌按服在地，口鼻受傷流血。其後多名軍裝警員接報到場，並調查該野豬如何闖入機場範圍。<br />\n<br />\n事件亦令網民嘖嘖稱奇，好奇牠是游水還是衝閘非法闖進，亦有網民對其受傷淌血表示關心，「真係慘慘豬！陰功豬！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161220/56070634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161220%2F56070634&d=9jjekClNMuLH3TYA%2FbvXeHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=db557db7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161220%2F56070634&h=48166fde\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161220/56070634</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161220/large/1482217332_ce7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161220%2Flarge%2F1482217332_ce7e.jpg&h=a06f502b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b49abd7ae6de7815adf74c6e90b756bdf45ccf61","tid":47192,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:44:26.000Z","msg":"成口血仲唔係監生打死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73359744e9d798d2f922160d3186452abfe35187","tid":47192,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:45:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"904cfe48d4155c0530ffe85e5c9373acbf03431d","tid":47192,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:46:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似曾相識，當年雨革都係咁對學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢班咪係佢地囉，唔係邊有得升做機場特警。"},{"pid":"1011662411c7dfcb4e75edee068f2118bab597d8","tid":47192,"uid":37651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:47:04.000Z","msg":"一定係本土豬"}]}